description:
Shake it up with these Puyo Puyo Maracas!
This accessory changes Amigo's maracas into Puyo Puyo Maracas!

This item is included in the Puyo Puyo Accessories Pack.
Purchasing the Puyo Puyo Accessories Pack will make this accessory available for your Amigo in the shop menu.
name: Puyo Puyo Maracas
